Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.74,0:23:33.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妮诺  男人只要抓住了他的胃袋就万事OK了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.88,0:23:34.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.47,0:23:35.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,首先要像挖坑一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.71,0:23:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,挖坑一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.50,0:23:38.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把拳头捅进去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.11,0:23:38.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,捅进去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.95,0:23:40.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下集  第6桥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.28,0:23:41.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第6桥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.04,0:23:43.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真不错  刚才你确实抓住胃袋了
